data.description: OPEN HOUSE SUN 12/3- 1:00-3:30  - 4 bedroom 2 1/2 bath home in Oak Hills School District.   A long driveway off of Revmal St. creates a quiet oasis in Delhi.   Spacious living room w/ large window leading into a dining room. The efficient kitchen is a culinary delight, w/ SS appliances, & ample cabinet space. Opens seamlessly to breakfast area and family room w/ large wood-burning FP, creating an ideal setting for intimate gatherings and larger celebrations. The upstairs master bedroom suite is 19x12 with an en-suite full bathroom, dressing room vanity area, and walk-in closet. Upstairs, you'll find three well-appointed bedrooms, each with its own unique charm, adjacent to an updated full hall bathroom.  New carpet, laminated flooring, and fresh paint throughout the 1st & 2nd fl. Step outside to the backyard, where you'll find a private 6 ft fenced outdoor landscaped yard for entertaining & and privacy. The lower level is a partially finished 2nd family room and laundry room.
